{"tid":677922,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港這一天　25-May-2018 土地大辯論變大鬧劇","createTime":"2018-05-25T15:21:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T15:21:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b525b148dec9d556ec546b0a784b944a0d930540","tid":677922,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T15:21:19.000Z","msg":"香港這一天　25-May-2018<br />\n土地大辯論變大鬧劇<br />\n<br />\n土地大辯論明日進入第二階段，展開問卷調查。市民可從問卷10個短中期及中長期土地供應選項內，揀選滿足1200公頃土地短缺的選項組合。有團體形容為「點心紙」問卷。楊健興分析大辯論遊戲；各位認為社會能否有共識。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hJ6ZVYF_Vyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhJ6ZVYF_Vyw&d=B3ifCGddofe07YKHAYxKP4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=2693debf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hJ6ZVYF_Vyw</a>"}]}